7.819">thing</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">“激情”不过是浮光掠影</span></p><p begin="00:27.839" end="00:31.701" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:27.839" end="00:28.176">It's</span> <span begin="00:28.508" end="00:28.733">ac</span><span begin="00:28.733" end="00:28.931">ci</span><span begin="00:29.034" end="00:29.856">den</span><span begin="00:29.856" end="00:30.149">tal</span> <span begin="00:30.533" end="00:30.780">chem</span><span begin="00:30.780" end="00:31.701">istry</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">一场阴差阳错的化学反应</span></p><p begin="00:32.878" end="00:36.578" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="00:32.878" end="00:33.234">Lus</span><span begin="00:33.234" end="00:33.325">t</span> <span begin="00:33.325" end="00:33.450">is</span> <span begin="00:33.450" end="00:33.597">a</span> <span begin="00:33.597" end="00:34.272">li</span><span begin="00:34.272" end="00:34.594">ar</span> <span begin="00:34.807" end="00:34.927">a</span> <span begin="00:34.927" end="00:35.313">short-</span><span begin="00:35.313" end="00:35.612">lived</span> <span begin="00:35.612" end="00:36.578">fire</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">“情欲”是个谎言 是转瞬即灭的野火</span></p><p begin="00:36.835" end="00:39.386" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="00:36.835" end="00:36.967">It</span> <span begin="00:36.967" end="00:37.183">ain't</span> <span begin="00:37.183" end="00:37.329">what</span> <span begin="00:37.329" end="00:37.517">you</span> <span begin="00:37.517" end="00:37.693">and</span> <span begin="00:37.693" end="00:38.019">I</span> <span begin="00:38.019" end="00:38.351">are</span> <span begin="00:38.351" end="00:38.745">at</span> <span begin="00:38.745" end="00:39.386">all</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">根本配不上你我之间的羁绊交错</span></p><p begin="00:40.700" end="00:46.632" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="00:40.700" end="00:41.753">Oh,</span> <span begin="00:42.063" end="00:42.343">it's</span> <span begin="00:42.343" end="00:42.746">a</span> <span begin="00:42.746" end="00:43.767">need,</span> <span begin="00:44.145" end="00:44.417">it's</span> <span begin="00:44.417" end="00:44.777">a</span> <span begin="00:44.777" end="00:46.632">need</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">噢 这是命中不可或缺 是灵魂所需</span></p><p begin="00:48.184" end="00:54.721" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="00:48.184" end="00:48.537">I</span> <span begin="00:48.537" end="00:48.785">would</span> <span begin="00:48.847" end="00:49.929">go</span> <span begin="00:50.210" end="00:50.429">a</span><span begin="00:50.429" end="00:50.866">ny</span><span begin="00:50.866" end="00:51.924">where</span> <span begin="00:52.252" end="00:52.494">that</span> <span begin="00:52.494" end="00:52.888">you</span> <span begin="00:52.888" end="00:54.721">lead</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">只要你指引方向 天涯海角我都追随</span></p><p begin="00:56.315" end="01:00.769" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="00:56.315" end="00:56.568">I</span> <span begin="00:56.568" end="00:56.882">am</span> <span begin="00:56.882" end="00:57.307">hope</span><span begin="00:57.307" end="00:57.776">less,</span> <span begin="00:57.929" end="00:58.350">breath</span><span begin="00:58.350" end="00:58.758">less,</span> <span begin="00:59.026" end="00:59.421">burn</span><span begin="00:59.421" end="00:59.741">ing</span> <span begin="00:59.934" end="01:00.769">slow</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我无可救药 屏住呼吸 任爱火慢熬</span></p><p begin="01:01.013" end="01:06.156" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="01:01.013" end="01:01.431">Touch</span> <span begin="01:01.431" end="01:01.785">me,</span> <span begin="01:01.998" end="01:02.420">hold</span> <span begin="01:02.420" end="01:02.774">me,</span> <span begin="01:03.029" end="01:03.460">tell</span> <span begin="01:03.460" end="01:03.796">me</span> <span begin="01:03.900" end="01:03.952">"</span><span begin="01:03.952" end="01:04.089">I</span> <span begin="01:04.089" end="01:04.488">won't</span> <span begin="01:04.488" end="01:04.741">let</span> <span begin="01:04.741" end="01:05.070">you</span> <span begin="01:05.109" end="01:06.156">go"</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">抚摸我 拥抱我 对我说“我绝不放手”</span></p><p begin="01:06.474" end="01:10.994" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="01:06.474" end="01:06.794">I</span> <span begin="01:06.794" end="01:07.118">won't</span> <span begin="01:07.118" end="01:08.121">leave,</span> <span begin="01:08.528" end="01:08.845">it's</span> <span begin="01:08.845" end="01:09.180">a</span> <span begin="01:09.180" end="01:10.994">need</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我不会离去 因为此生非你不可</span></p><p begin="01:13.256" end="01:16.957" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="01:13.256" end="01:13.622">Dan</span><span begin="01:13.622" end="01:13.926">ger</span> <span begin="01:13.926" end="01:14.285">is</span> <span begin="01:14.285" end="01:14.573">a</span> <span begin="01:14.573" end="01:14.947">thou</span><span begin="01:14.947" end="01:15.214">sand</span> <span begin="01:15.214" end="01:15.587">prick</span><span begin="01:15.627" end="01:15.988">les</span> <span begin="01:15.988" end="01:16.296">on</span> <span begin="01:16.296" end="01:16.602">my</span> <span begin="01:16.679" end="01:16.957">neck</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">“危险”是颈间千百根刺扎的寒意</span></p><p begin="01:16.979" end="01:20.346" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="01:16.979" end="01:17.191">That</span> <span begin="01:17.259" end="01:17.694">tell</span> <span begin="01:17.694" end="01:17.895">me</span> <span begin="01:17.944" end="01:18.327">to</span> <span begin="01:18.327" end="01:18.661">run</span> <span begin="01:18.688" end="01:18.968">or</span> <span begin="01:19.008" end="01:19.315">to</span> <span begin="01:19.315" end="01:20.114">free</span><span begin="01:20.114" end="01:20.346">ze</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:la